{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/WLS2-gui-hi-dpi/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Discreater Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9046c7f7-96b8-577f-b723-7f9405d78bb3","excerpt":"在WSL2中启用GUI 参考 WSL github issue #4106 准备 本篇文章只适用于WSL2。WSL1的解决方案比较简单，网上的教程也很多，所以不再多讲。 首先在cmd或powershell中确认WSL的版本号为2 确定主机IP 把下面一行写入或者(根据你的shell而定) 安装VcXsrv…","html":"<h1>在WSL2中启用GUI</h1>\n<h2>参考</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/WSL/issues/4106\">WSL github issue #4106</a></p>\n<h2>准备</h2>\n<p>本篇文章只适用于WSL2。WSL1的解决方案比较简单，网上的教程也很多，所以不再多讲。</p>\n<p>首先在cmd或powershell中确认WSL的版本号为2</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\"><pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\"><span class=\"token function\">PS</span> C:\\> wsl <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>l <span class=\"token operator\">--</span>all <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>v\n  NAME            STATE           VERSION\n<span class=\"token operator\">*</span> Ubuntu<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>18<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>04    Running         2</code></pre></div>\n<h2>确定主机IP</h2>\n<p>把下面一行写入<code class=\"language-text\">~/.bashrc</code>或者<code class=\"language-text\">~/.zshrc</code>(根据你的shell而定)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\"><span class=\"token environment constant\">DISPLAY</span></span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">`</span><span class=\"token function\">cat</span> /etc/resolv.conf <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">grep</span> nameserver <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">awk</span> <span class=\"token string\">'{print <span class=\"token variable\">$2</span>}'</span><span class=\"token variable\">`</span></span>:0.0</code></pre></div>\n<h2>安装VcXsrv</h2>\n<p>可以从sourceforge上下载安装包：<a href=\"https://sourceforge.net/projects/vcxsrv/\">https://sourceforge.net/projects/vcxsrv/</a>，一般来说默认安装即可。</p>\n<h2>启动</h2>\n<p>安装完成后点击Xlaunch启动，如图所示\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 510px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0135f716dbb26806af6ca0602b4503c9/0abdd/xlaunch1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 81.08108108108108%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"xlaunch-1\"\n        title=\"xlaunch-1\"\n        src=\"/static/0135f716dbb26806af6ca0602b4503c9/0abdd/xlaunch1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0135f716dbb26806af6ca0602b4503c9/12f09/xlaunch1.png 148w,\n/static/0135f716dbb26806af6ca0602b4503c9/e4a3f/xlaunch1.png 295w,\n/static/0135f716dbb26806af6ca0602b4503c9/0abdd/xlaunch1.png 510w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 510px) 100vw, 510px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n4个模式的效果很容易看出来，看不出来也可以自己一个个试，选择自己习惯的就行。点击下一步\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 510px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/27cd9ebec355a4fb438f905ac400a57a/0abdd/xlaunch2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 81.08108108108108%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"xlaunch-2\"\n        title=\"xlaunch-2\"\n        src=\"/static/27cd9ebec355a4fb438f905ac400a57a/0abdd/xlaunch2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/27cd9ebec355a4fb438f905ac400a57a/12f09/xlaunch2.png 148w,\n/static/27cd9ebec355a4fb438f905ac400a57a/e4a3f/xlaunch2.png 295w,\n/static/27cd9ebec355a4fb438f905ac400a57a/0abdd/xlaunch2.png 510w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 510px) 100vw, 510px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n直接点击下一步\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 510px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e88c44be7e55e0d3fcc68500aed734aa/0abdd/xlaunch3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 81.08108108108108%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"xlaunch-3\"\n        title=\"xlaunch-3\"\n        src=\"/static/e88c44be7e55e0d3fcc68500aed734aa/0abdd/xlaunch3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e88c44be7e55e0d3fcc68500aed734aa/12f09/xlaunch3.png 148w,\n/static/e88c44be7e55e0d3fcc68500aed734aa/e4a3f/xlaunch3.png 295w,\n/static/e88c44be7e55e0d3fcc68500aed734aa/0abdd/xlaunch3.png 510w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 510px) 100vw, 510px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n注意这里要勾选<code class=\"language-text\">Disable access control</code>，然后点击下一步\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 510px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ab80043c88331c5756b93c81bdf45bb1/0abdd/xlaunch4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 81.08108108108108%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"xlaunch-4\"\n        title=\"xlaunch-4\"\n        src=\"/static/ab80043c88331c5756b93c81bdf45bb1/0abdd/xlaunch4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ab80043c88331c5756b93c81bdf45bb1/12f09/xlaunch4.png 148w,\n/static/ab80043c88331c5756b93c81bdf45bb1/e4a3f/xlaunch4.png 295w,\n/static/ab80043c88331c5756b93c81bdf45bb1/0abdd/xlaunch4.png 510w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 510px) 100vw, 510px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n这里的保存配置会生成一个文件并让你选择保存的位置，推荐保存，下一次启动的时候就可以直接启动这个配置文件（也可以在命令行里打开）。点击完成之后，在右下角托盘区就会有VcXsrv的图标，表示已经启动。</p>\n<h2>防火墙配置</h2>\n<p>实际上这样子还不能启动gui，试图启动的时候会被Windows的防火墙阻止。可以直接关掉防火墙，或者用在管理员模式的powershell里输入下面的命令：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\"><pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\"><span class=\"token function\">Set-NetFirewallProfile</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Name public <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>DisabledInterfaceAliases <span class=\"token string\">\"vEthernet (WSL)\"</span> </code></pre></div>\n<p>这个命令指挥关掉WSL的虚拟局域网的防火墙。</p>\n<h2>保存为脚本</h2>\n<p>为方便使用，可以把这行命令保存成脚本，后缀为.ps1，例如<code class=\"language-text\">G:\\\\Scripts\\\\disableWSLFirewall.ps1</code>，但是powershell的管理员权限脚本会限制直接运行，可以再套一个cmd脚本，内容是提升权限运行powershell脚本</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cmd\"><pre class=\"language-cmd\"><code class=\"language-cmd\">Powershell.exe -executionpolicy remotesigned -File G:\\Scripts\\disableWSLFirewall.ps1</code></pre></div>\n<p>里面的路径需要换成你的ps1脚本路径。另外，如果你也保存了VcXsrv的脚本的话，也可以直接在这个cmd脚本中添加VcXsrv脚本的路径。\n所以我的cmd脚本<code class=\"language-text\">wslGui.bat</code>内容如下</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cmd\"><pre class=\"language-cmd\"><code class=\"language-cmd\">Powershell.exe -executionpolicy remotesigned -File G:\\Scripts\\disableWSLFirewall.ps1\nG:\\Scripts\\multiWindow.xlaunch</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>注意</strong>：这个脚本的运行需要以管理员模式，并且需要在启动过一次WSL之后才会有效（Windows重启以后，WSL启动之前，是不存在WSL的虚拟局域网的，所以这时候脚本会报错）。</p>\n<h2>HiDPI的设置</h2>\n<p>在高分屏下(Win10 显示设置中的缩放比率大于100%），VcXsrv的显示会模糊，这不只是WSL的原因，我目前的解决办法是让VcXsrv使用100%的缩放。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>首先找到VcXsrv.exe的位置，右键开始菜单中的Xlaunch图标，<code class=\"language-text\">更多</code>-><code class=\"language-text\">打开文件位置</code>，找到Xlaunch的快捷方式的位置</li>\n<li>然后右键这个快捷方式，点击<code class=\"language-text\">打开文件所在的位置</code></li>\n<li>在打开的目录里找到<code class=\"language-text\">vcxsrv.exe</code>这个文件，右键-><code class=\"language-text\">属性</code></li>\n<li>选择<code class=\"language-text\">兼容性</code>选项卡，点击<code class=\"language-text\">更改高DPI设置</code></li>\n<li>在弹出的窗口中修改下面的选项<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/766a22e6a8abc8aa3b0da39a0876fcb7/0098c/vcxsrv.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 82.43243243243244%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"vcxsrv\"\n        title=\"vcxsrv\"\n        src=\"/static/766a22e6a8abc8aa3b0da39a0876fcb7/fcda8/vcxsrv.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/766a22e6a8abc8aa3b0da39a0876fcb7/12f09/vcxsrv.png 148w,\n/static/766a22e6a8abc8aa3b0da39a0876fcb7/e4a3f/vcxsrv.png 295w,\n/static/766a22e6a8abc8aa3b0da39a0876fcb7/fcda8/vcxsrv.png 590w,\n/static/766a22e6a8abc8aa3b0da39a0876fcb7/0098c/vcxsrv.png 775w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>\n<p>确定，搞定</p>\n<p>15.7寸笔记本100%分辨率对于对我来说还能勉强看，至于选择清晰的字体还是大的字体，这取决于你自己了。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>由于代理出现的异常</h2>\n<p>说个和GUI无关的事。有时候会因为代理的原因导致WSL无法启动，出现<code class=\"language-text\">参考的对象类型不支持尝试的操作。</code>，这时候用管理员模式运行<code class=\"language-text\">netsh winsock reset</code>即可（会提示重启，但是实际上不需要重启），参考 <a href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/WSL/issues/4194\">WSL github issue #4194</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"在WSL2中启用GUI","date":"2020-03-22"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/WLS2-gui-hi-dpi/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/JS-bit-operator/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"JS 按位操作符溢出问题"}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["1262554966","2199005656","695495319"]}